{"tid":1954300,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]異世界女神物語(6）無人開PO既","createTime":"2020-04-01T17:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T01:57:08.000Z","uid":204571,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cec25542a6bb9cbd2bd751cedc904c7b852baa","tid":1954300,"uid":204571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQ.主角有冇用？洗唔洗升架？<br />\nA.話明異世界女神，你話洗唔洗升啦？<br />\n<br />\nQ.洗唔洗刷首抽？邊隻最好？<br />\nA.基本上你當每個ac有30抽當首抽<br />\n推薦既有以下呢幾隻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7cYfiJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7cYfiJ2.png&h=ed142ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓦爾基里 : 外號瓦妹，女武神<br />\nT1坦克無論PVE、PVP都係好強勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSN4b35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSN4b35.png&h=0dc84e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莉莉絲 ：外號 llc<br />\nT0級別刺客 PVP、PVE皆有一席之地<br />\n基本上無唔抽既理由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Khz6qpb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhz6qpb.png&h=07161b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅林 ： 外號 地圖炮<br />\nT0級別法師 PVE最強&quot;法系輸出&quot;無庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkNosCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkNosCA.jpg&h=8474c635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德古拉 ： 外號 吸血鬼<br />\nT0級別坦克、無論係50%減傷鍊子或者自身50%魔防分享比隊友，吸血鬼都係你必要既選擇<br />\n<br />\n路西法： 外號 街場掛機咪撚用<br />\nT1級別刺客 夠七日就會送<br />\n一刀一隻好爽 但唔洗刷首抽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaQOE3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaQOE3V.png&h=10729fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿提米斯 ：外號 暗弓<br />\n現時版本pvp 強角<br />\n天生技每3/4 turn 就自己隨機攻擊對方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rAY8E40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrAY8E40.png&h=fec14783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嫦娥 <br />\nPvp pvp 都好用<br />\nPvp 最好五星 六星就最好<br />\n招燈有減傷同嘲諷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">陣容</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n因應唔同時候就用唔同既隊<br />\n主要分守護(坦)，刺客，戰士，法師，射手，神官(奶)<br />\n<br />\n守護<br />\n瓦妹&gt;波賽頓&gt;馬可波羅<br />\n<br />\n刺客<br />\n莉莉絲 &gt; 路西法 &gt; 服部 : 小丑<br />\n<br />\n法師<br />\n梅林 &gt; 整個世界<br />\n當然睇你玩咩隊，有毒隊之類就用蛇女 洛基<br />\n<br />\n戰士<br />\n米迦勒 = 火隊<br />\n哈帝斯 = pve 半血收頭<br />\n暫時比較少會放戰士住<br />\n<br />\n射手<br />\n現版本一定係暗弓<br />\nstrong hold抽暗弓 = 世界更美好<br />\n<br />\n神官<br />\n雅典娜 = 不死buff<br />\n伊莎貝拉 = 加盾 大奶<br />\n維納斯 = SR恩物<br />\n嫦娥 = 減傷 嘲諷<br />\n<br />\n組隊建議呢到就唔放，留返空間比大家自行發掘<br />\n小弟個陣係<br />\n莉莉絲 梅林 伊莎貝拉 瓦妹 吸血鬼<br />\n支援 愛麗絲 阿波羅 維納斯<br />\n<br />\n抽到暗弓就抽伊莎貝拉換落去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">體力分配</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n主線推到無得推就打星輝刷素材升裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdRD01T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdRD01T.jpg&h=714617fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刷圖書館都得，升秘技<br />\n器靈石 有速度必留！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">裝備</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">所有的裝備都可以練、<del>40等前可無痛分解！</del> 輪迴後嘅裝都可以100% 復原<br />\n請勿執著於一定要ssr先練！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武器：<br />\n赫拉的嘆息(pvp.pve)、海皇三叉戟(pvp)、諸神葬歌(pve.pvp)、龍惑(pve)、烏勒爾的野望(pvp)、噬神之宿命(pvp.pve)、煉獄裁斷(pvp.pve)、死神黑鐮刃(pvp.pve)、龍魂守護者(pvp.pve)、滅烈之主(pvp.pve)<br />\n<br />\n防具：<br />\n光輝界的救贖、聖皇法衣、彌賽亞祭袍、星輝聖袍、不死鳥鎖甲、炎龍魔鎧、贖罪鎮魂鎧、星輝起源、哲人王假面、赫拉的花冠、終焉之榮耀、羽蛇神復仇、風切之翼、吸血鬼之吻、冥王盔、宙斯盾(以上副本、對戰都好用)<br />\n<br />\n飾品：<br />\n審判的號角(後期無用)、星輝閃耀、德羅普尼爾、奧義的魔盾(雙面刃)、霜巨人之心、索爾鐵手套、阿奴達銀臂、聖鳥古迪、時序沙漏、龍血瓶、冥后耳環。(飾品是本遊戲極度缺乏既一樣野)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更新幾張畢業裝嘅大圖，殘體注意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S2gZ7E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S2gZ7E.png&h=cb91b448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TwY0Hk1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTwY0Hk1.png&h=4287a2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9yDt01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9yDt01.png&h=66140807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公會任務速刷教學：(會員 #131637 界咸村民提供)<br />\n1.一場上一隻角色<br />\n2.按入去時有按英雄可以換裝<br />\n3.準備好一套最勁既物傷裝同魔傷裝<br />\n4.輪流用全部角色打（記住要換裝、裝秘技同石頭）<br />\n5.石頭有個儲存功能，物功我用莉莉絲既裝，魔攻用梅林<br />\n<br />\n6.開心準時星期一入手SSR裝<br />\nD卒仔唔使點覺醒用左神裝都1打10，有AOE更佳，唔使一下一隻"},{"pid":"555b4b428fbcd108681e81dae01b12ef9f55f23c","tid":1954300,"uid":4263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"剛剛入坑 留個名先"},{"pid":"b2601b2bd0f9cd29487b4c8bc27fd751e50ce813","tid":1954300,"uid":349904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T18:29:51.000Z","msg":"就執，所以無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670f5451128ba9f310d85beff86207677373abc0","tid":1954300,"uid":349904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555b4b428fbcd108681e81dae01b12ef9f55f23c","tid":1954300,"uid":4263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"剛剛入坑 留個名先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T18:30:38.000Z","msg":"呢排太悶，搵唔到驚玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fe441107f98426ccc8e0680f157e4c1698dfec","tid":1954300,"uid":4263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670f5451128ba9f310d85beff86207677373abc0","tid":1954300,"uid":349904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"